From f05f728327f30037567cb79725120a498cb0848b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Paul Sajna <hello@paulsajna.com>
Date: Tue, 29 Jul 2025 19:14:33 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Added BlackBerry KEY2 model and its US English layout

Added [BlackBerry KEY2] model and its corresponding vendor-specific US English layout.

Sources:
- Phone:
  - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BlackBerry_Key2
  - https://wiki.postmarketos.org/wiki/BlackBerry_KEY2_Generic_(blackberry-key2-generic)
- Keyboard:
  - Photo of keypad: https://wiki.postmarketos.org/images/thumb/f/f0/BlackBerry_KEY2_keyboard.jpg/600px-BlackBerry_KEY2_keyboard.jpg
  - Layer 5 on "sym" key, mapped as ralt: https://wiki.postmarketos.org/images/thumb/a/af/BlackBerry_KEY2_SYM_Keys.png/600px-BlackBerry_KEY2_SYM_Keys.png

Part-of: <https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/xkeyboard-config/xkeyboard-config/-/merge_requests/856>
---
 changes/models/+856-blackberry-key2.md |  4 +++
 rules/base.xml                         |  7 ++++
 rules/rules.in                         |  1 +
 symbols/blackberry_vndr/key2/us        | 47 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 4 files changed, 59 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 changes/models/+856-blackberry-key2.md
 create mode 100644 symbols/blackberry_vndr/key2/us

diff --git a/changes/models/+856-blackberry-key2.md b/changes/models/+856-blackberry-key2.md
